window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Elite soldier turned dragon hunter.</b></p> <p>Cursed by a blind witch in a remote corner of Waristan, Special Ops Captain Jason Wolfe finds himself transforming into a creature of local legend, a lupine referred to in fearful whispers as Blue Wolf.</p> <p>Faster, stronger, and more lethal, he’s the perfect soldier - but not for the US military. To break the curse, Jason must join a war between ancient tribal foes: blue werewolves and the formidable White Dragon.</p> <p>In a battle spanning from the peaks of Central Asia to the valleys of Manhattan, and with the help of a bookish wizard named Prof Croft, Jason will push himself to the breaking point. Because with the curse now spreading to his mind, he’s running out of time - and the stakes couldn’t be higher:</p> <p>Win and he returns home to his fiancé, his family, and a future.</p> <p>Lose and he dies a bloodthirsty beast....</p> <p><b>Books in the Strangeverse:</b></p> <p>Blue Wolf Series</p> <ul> <li>Book 1: <i>Blue Curse</i> - More to come!</li> </ul> <p>Prof Croft Series</p> <ul> <li>Book 0: <i>Book of Souls</i> (prequel)</li> <li>Book 1: <i>Demon Moon</i></li> <li>Book 2: <i>Blood Deal</i></li> <li>Book 3: <i>Purge City</i></li> <li>Book 4: <i>Death Mage</i></li> </ul>"; 
